[0.198, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[1.011, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;38;2;232;162;23mQuery Operators\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nA comprehensive reference of query operators used across all ServiceNow query APIs\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mQuery Operators\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mQuery Operators\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  These operators are used across all ServiceNow query APIs to filter and retrieve records. They work consistently whether you're using:\r\n  - **[GlideRecord](/docs/gliderecord/)** – The standard server-side API for database operations\r\n  - **[GlideRecordSecure](/docs/gliderecordsecure/)** – GlideRecord with ACL enforcement\r\n  - **[GlideQuery](/docs/glidequery/)** – The modern, expressive alternative to GlideRecord\r\n  - **[GlideAggregate](/docs/glideaggregate/)** – For database aggregation queries (COUNT, SUM, MIN, MAX, AVG)\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mUsing Operators\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mIn GlideRecord & GlideRecordSecure\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Use operators with `addQuery()` or `addEncodedQuery()`:\r\n  var gr = new GlideRecord('incident');\r\n  gr.addQuery('priority', '<=', 2);\r\n  gr.addQuery('state', 'IN', '1,2');\r\n  gr.query();\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mIn GlideQuery\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  Pass operators as the second argument in `where()`:\r\n  new GlideQuery('incident')\r\n  .where('priority', '<=', 2)\r\n  .where('state', 'IN', [1, 2])\r\n  .select();\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1mIn GlideAggregate\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  Operators work the same as GlideRecord:\r\n  var ga = new GlideAggregate('incident');\r\n  ga.addQuery('priority', '<=', 2);"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n  ga.addAggregate('COUNT');\r\n  ga.query();\r\n  ---\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mOperator Reference\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | Operator label           | Equivalent query operator | Example query                                                                 |\r\n  | ------------------------ | ------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is not                   | `!=`                      | `short_description!=Network storage unavailable`                              |\r\n  | and                      | `^`                       | `active=true^CallerISNOTEMPTY`                                                |\r\n  | OR filter (new query)    | `^NQ`                     | `active=true^NQactive=false`                                                  |"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | OR condition             | `^OR`                     | `short_descriptionISEMPTY^ORdescriptionISEMPTY`                               |\r\n  | before                   | `<`                       | `sla_due<javascript:gs.daysAgoStart(0)`                                       |\r\n  | less than                | `<`                       | `reassignment_count<2`                                                        |\r\n  | at or before             | `<=`                      | `sla_due<=javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)`                                        |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | less than or is          | `<=`                      | `short_description<=s`                                                        |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is                       | `=`                       | `short_description=Network storage unavailable`                               |\r\n  | after                    | `>`                       | `sla_due>javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)`                                         |\r\n  | greater than             | `>`                       | `impact>2`                                                                    |\r\n  | at or after              | `>=`                      | `sla_due>=javascript:gs.daysAgoStart(0)`                                      |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | greater than or is       | `>=`                      | `short_description>=s`                                                        |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is anything              | `ANYTHING`                | `short_descriptionANYTHING`                                                   |\r\n  | between                  | `BETWEEN`                 | `short_descriptionBETWEENq@t`                                                 |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | between                  | `BETWEEN`                 | `impactBETWEEN1@2`                                                            |\r\n  | between                  | `BETWEEN`                 | `sla_dueBETWEENjavascript:gs.daysAgoStart(1)@javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)`     |\r\n  | between                  | `BETWEEN`                 | `reassignment_countBETWEEN1@2`                                                |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | changes from             | `CHANGESFROM`             | `stateCHANGESFROM4^EQ`                                                        |\r\n  | changes to               | `CHANGESTO`               | `stateCHANGESTO4^EQ`                                                          |\r\n  | trend (after)            | `DATEPART`                | `sla_dueDATEPARTMonday@javascript:gs.datePart('dayofweek','monday','GT')`     |\r\n  | trend (before)           | `DATEPART`                | `sla_dueDATEPARTMonday@javascript:gs.datePart('dayofweek','monday','LT')`     |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | trend (on or after)      | `DATEPART`                | `sla_dueDATEPARTMonday@javascript:gs.datePart('dayofweek','monday','GE')`     |\r\n  | trend (on or before)     | `DATEPART`                | `sla_dueDATEPARTMonday@javascript:gs.datePart('dayofweek','monday','LE')`     |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | trend (on)               | `DATEPART`                | `sla_dueDATEPARTMonday@javascript:gs.datePart('dayofweek','monday','EE')`     |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is (dyanmic)             | `DYNAMIC`                 | `caller_idDYNAMIC54635e965f510100a9ad2572f2b4774c`                            |\r\n  | is empty string          | `EMPTYSTRING`             | `caller_idEMPTYSTRING`                                                        |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | ends with                | `ENDSWITH`                | `short_descriptionENDSWITHoutage`                                             |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | greater than field       | `GT_FIELD`                | `reassignment_countGT_FIELDreopen_count`                                      |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | greater than or is field | `GT_OR_EQUALS_FIELD`      | `reassignment_countGT_OR_EQUALS_FIELDreopen_count`                            |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is one of                | `IN`                      | `impactIN1,2`                                                                 |\r\n  | is empty                 | `ISEMPTY`                 | `short_descriptionISEMPTY`                                                    |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is not empty             | `ISNOTEMPTY`              | `activeISNOTEMPTY`                                                            |\r\n  | is less than             | `LESSTHAN`                | `sla_dueLESSTHANactivity_due@day@before@3`                                    |\r\n  | contains                 | `LIKE`                    | `subcategoryLIKEem`                                                           |\r\n  | less than field          | `LT_FIELD`                | `reassignment_countLT_FIELDreopen_count`                                      |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | less than or is field    | `LT_OR_EQUALS_FIELD`      | `reassignment_countLT_OR_EQUALS_FIELDreopen_count`                            |\r\n  | is more than             | `MORETHAN`                | `sla_dueMORETHANactivity_due@day@before@1`                                    |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is not one of            | `NOT IN`                  | `subcategoryNOT INdb2,sql server,oracle`                                      |\r\n  | does not contain         | `NOT LIKE`                | `subcategoryNOT LIKEem`                                                       |\r\n  | not on                   | `NOTONToday`              | `sla_dueNOTONToday@javascript:gs.daysAgoStart(0)@javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)` |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is different             | `NSAMEAS`                 | `activeNSAMEASmade_sla`                                                       |\r\n  | on                       | `ONToday`                 | `sla_dueONToday@javascript:gs.daysAgoStart(0)@javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)`    |\r\n  | relative (on)            | `RELATIVEEE`              | `sla_dueRELATIVEEE@hour@ago@1`                                                |\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  | relative (on or after)   | `RELATIVEGE`              | `sla_dueRELATIVEGE@hour@ago@1`                                                |\r\n  | relative (after)         | `RELATIVEGT`              | `sla_dueRELATIVEGT@hour@ago@1`                                                |\r\n  | relative (on or before)  | `RELATIVELE`              | `sla_dueRELATIVELE@hour@ago@1`                                                |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | relative (before)        | `RELATIVELT`              | `sla_dueRELATIVELT@hour@ago@1`                                                |\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  | is same                  | `SAMEAS`                  | `short_descriptionSAMEASdescription`                                          |\r\n  | starts with              | `STARTSWITH`              | `subcategorySTARTSWITHem`                                                     |\r\n  | changes                  | `VALCHANGES`              | `stateVALCHANGES`                                                             |\r\n  ---\r\n  *Source: [https://sn.jace.pro/docs/operators/](https://sn.jace.pro/docs/operators/) - ServiceNow Documentation by Jace Benson*\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mExamples\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mvar gr = new GlideRecord('incident');\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mgr.addQuery('priority', '<=', 2);\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mgr.addQuery('state', 'IN', '1,2');\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mgr.query();\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mnew GlideQuery('incident')\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0m  .where('priority', '<=', 2)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0m  .where('state', 'IN', [1, 2])\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0m  .select();\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mvar ga = new GlideAggregate('incident');\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mga.addQuery('priority', '<=', 2);\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mga.addAggregate('COUNT');\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[38;2;0;255;0mga.query();\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[38;2;136;136;136m-----\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;136;136;136mSource: sn.jace.pro\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
